s.\u201d<\/strong><br \/><a rel=\"nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"https:\/\/www.routerprotocol.com\/\"><strong>\u2013 Ramani Ramachandran, Co-Founder &amp; CEO of Router Protocol<\/strong><\/a><\/p>\n<\/blockquote>\n<p>Recently, Router Protocol introduced a <a rel=\"nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"https:\/\/explorer.routerprotocol.com\/\" data-cke-saved-href=\"https:\/\/explorer.routerprotocol.com\/\">cross-chain explorer<\/a> which eliminates the need to monitor different block explorers to track cross-chain transactions.<\/p>\n<p><strong>Note, Router Protocol has several developments in the pipeline to be released in the near future:<\/strong><\/p>\n<p><strong>1. More L1 and L2 chain integrations:<\/strong><\/p>\n<ul>\n<li>Introduction of EVM-compatible chains including Arbitrum, Optimism, Harmony, Aurora, Moonbeam, and Cronos.<\/li>\n<li>Integration of non-EMV-compatible chains such as Terra and Solana.<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<p><strong>2. A Router Protocol cross-chain SDK to facilitate a more convenient cross-chain development environment<\/strong><\/p>\n<p><strong>3. An incentivized liquidity mining campaign to reward Router\u2019s liquidity providers.<\/strong><\/p>\n<aside class=\"mashsb-container mashsb-main mashsb-stretched\">\n                <\/aside>\n<p>            <!-- Share buttons by mashshare.net - Version: 3.8.1-->\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/p>\n<div class=\"jeg_post_source\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<span>Source:<\/span><br \/>\n\t\t\t\t\t<a rel=\"nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http:\/\/www.routerprotocol.com\/\">RouterProtocol.com<\/a>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n<\/p><\/div>\n<p><br \/>\n<br \/><a href=\"https:\/\/www.cryptoninjas.net\/2022\/03\/30\/cross-chain-liquidity-aggregation-app-router-protocol-integrates-ethereum-and-fantom\/\">Source link <\/a><\/p>\n","protected":false},"excerpt":{"rendered":"<p>Router Protocol, an infrastructure layer enabling communication between blockchains, today announced it has added Ethereum and Fantom to its 